summary: April 20 is the 110th day of the year  in the Gregorian calendar.
full_text: Funny Cide  is a Thoroughbred race horse who won the Kentucky Derby and the Preakness Stakes in 2003. He is the first New York-bred horse to win the Kentucky Derby and the first gelding to win since Clyde Van Dusen in 1929.
title: Funny Cide
